; !!! YOUR MAIN PROGRAM MUST DECLARE BOTH:
;        %option no_sysinit
;        %zpreserved $02,$5f
; no_sysinit: a CXGEOS app is a GUEST -- the kernel owns the machine.
; Prog8's default startup (init_system) does a full reset -- RESTOR,
